         <abstract>Founded by David Davis Walker, Frank
                Ely, and others in 1883, based in St. Louis, Missouri. The company was acquired by
                Burlington Industries, Inc., in 1955. Minutes of meetings of stockholders and of directors,
                financial statements, account books, and other legal and administrative documents of
                a firm that manufactured, converted, and distributed cotton fabrics and hosiery,
                whose general office was located in St. Louis, Missouri.</abstract>
         
